{"tid":404442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［龍門］何君堯'殺無赦'論　袁國強：不可憑一兩字說是否犯法　要看字句背景","createTime":"2017-09-18T06:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T06:27:18.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2833695cd836e7939054db12e0c6c3c8d66146","tid":404442,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"立法會議員何君堯昨日在添馬公園發起集會，其間站台的屏山鄉事委員會主席曾樹和高叫，提倡港獨者應「殺」，何君堯即和應說「無赦」，更指「（搞港獨）啲人唔殺咗佢做咩」，引起關注。律政司長袁國強今中午見記者時表示，不評論個別事件，但指是否構成違反刑事法「要整體去睇」。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n袁國強解釋說，「語言的話，要睇講字句及背景，不可單憑一兩個字，亦要睇當時用這個字或說話嘅意思係點」，強調法庭會參考整個背景再作結論。至於是否有需要作進一步行動，他說「用返法庭用嘅原則」。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，若然有任何人認為需要跟進事件，可以依照一貫程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n袁國強另強調，「港獨」不符香港憲制及法律地位，看不到這時候鼓吹「港獨」對香港有任何好處。他續說，香港現時面對很多問題，認為聚焦討論其他問題更有建設性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710862542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710862542&d=dBg6tSW81F0Leg6ahdWzMY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=1315e0a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170918%2Fs00001%2F1505710862542&h=9618060d\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170918/s00001/1505710862542</a>"},{"pid":"12bcf21a9c6ce4e610354a12fa15d8a72b7c79df","tid":404442,"uid":2854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"「重奪」 惡啲定「殺」惡啲"},{"pid":"ce469f0a6ef5f661796dd92820a009146fc906aa","tid":404442,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"龍門任佢搬"},{"pid":"585b15ed9079a46eb74050d330ff4a7190db38a0","tid":404442,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:10:37.000Z","msg":"有人話要殺人，我好驚驚呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7db945ba0f13ed9a80405775eab14563f021794","tid":404442,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:12:09.000Z","msg":"不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"147e67918b35799eb5ab35e05836142e7b00eb1a","tid":404442,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:13:02.000Z","msg":"咁講法, 「做港共殺無赦」都得啦"},{"pid":"ceea05bf86a6c5f33435605a55870e15080d09f6","tid":404442,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"落街去同班廢老講 殺港獨廢捐無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n何大狀同袁司長講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddda9df8e0b66b39e7f77b07a412ec7bbb8c903","tid":404442,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:14:01.000Z","msg":"殺人都唔犯法？"},{"pid":"ddda904ec386d32c0e9f572a16052228675aaab7","tid":404442,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>袁國強解釋說，「語言的話，要睇講字句及背景，不可單憑一兩個字，亦要睇當時用這個字或說話嘅意思係點」，強調法庭會參考整個背景再作結論。至於是否有需要作進一步行動，他說「用返法庭用嘅原則」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你交比殖民地法官判啦"},{"pid":"a0839fef2f17583f5bb598b55d769baca3acc232","tid":404442,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:16:36.000Z","msg":"强國猿縱容殺人言論呀！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acff789918ed25dfca49813f00d134c0b64f26d4","tid":404442,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>「重奪」 惡啲定「殺」惡啲</blockquote><br />\n反共既講奪要坐監<br />\n奶共講到要殺人放火都唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n依種就係香港而家既「法治」<br />\n加埋有強國袁依條大仆街"},{"pid":"3b5f9cef58e763595554fe9d40b0f56ac8b2f84e","tid":404442,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T06:18:42.000Z","msg":